  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/d5e2883485c45cd6f86260d07431891e.poster.avif?t=1750039177\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/d5e2883485c45cd6f86260d07431891e.webm?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/d5e2883485c45cd6f86260d07431891e.mp4?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You are Shin, a demon hunter with no memory of his past. After striking an unusual partnership with Lux, a demon with the ability to shapeshift into a sword and manipulate time, you begin a quest to learn what happened to you and your loved ones. Fight brutal battles against terrible demons. Explore a corrupted and dangerous world. Regain what was once yours.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/db4219e5637a8d4439744c134fa0b999.poster.avif?t=1750039177\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/db4219e5637a8d4439744c134fa0b999.webm?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/db4219e5637a8d4439744c134fa0b999.mp4?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Gameplay Overview</strong><br>The Demon Sword, Lux, offers a wide array of utilities. Not only can she perform powerful attacks and shield you from harm, but she can also act as a platform and restore objects from the past. Use your demonic companion to survive in a desolate, demon-ridden Osaka.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/45346a6640e0f9437e4e660b3a0d927e.poster.avif?t=1750039177\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/45346a6640e0f9437e4e660b3a0d927e.webm?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/45346a6640e0f9437e4e660b3a0d927e.mp4?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As Shin defeats demons and levels up, new skills can be unlocked via the skill tree. Unlock the \"Warp\" skill to travel anywhere on the map or the double-jump skill to get up to higher ledges and explore new locations with ease.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/dd2c4415932a48feafb96c6fd1dc340c.poster.avif?t=1750039177\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/dd2c4415932a48feafb96c6fd1dc340c.webm?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/dd2c4415932a48feafb96c6fd1dc340c.mp4?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But Lux isn't the only weapon in your arsenal. In addition to firearms, Shin can also wield weapons such as greatswords and whips. Experiment with a variety of armaments and create your own style of combat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/d093b53b596a4da29330be61a7257fc6.poster.avif?t=1750039177\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/d093b53b596a4da29330be61a7257fc6.webm?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/d093b53b596a4da29330be61a7257fc6.mp4?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Enjoy the latest metroidvania from Team Ladybug, the team behind such acclaimed titles as \"Touhou Luna Nights\" and \"Record of Lodoss War: Deedlit in Wonder Labyrinth.\"<br><br>Explore a map far larger than past Team Ladybug projects, filled with side quests that both deepen your connection to and expand upon the world of \"Blade Chimera.\"<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/22318bf811e0f4988293ca97c51a129a.poster.avif?t=1750039177\" width=620 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/22318bf811e0f4988293ca97c51a129a.webm?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/22318bf811e0f4988293ca97c51a129a.mp4?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The Story</strong><br>It all began with the sudden appearance of a ghastly demonic horde. Humans fought against ghouls and ghosts in what would later be known as the \"Demon War,\" and the world was changed forever.<br><br>Thirty years later, using their expertise in combating demons, a religious group called the \"Holy Union\" has carved out a small but stable enclave of survivors.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/d5e2883485c45cd6f86260d07431891e.poster.avif?t=1750039177\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/d5e2883485c45cd6f86260d07431891e.webm?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/d5e2883485c45cd6f86260d07431891e.mp4?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You are Shin, a demon hunter with no memory of his past. After striking an unusual partnership with Lux, a demon with the ability to shapeshift into a sword and manipulate time, you begin a quest to learn what happened to you and your loved ones. Fight brutal battles against terrible demons. Explore a corrupted and dangerous world. Regain what was once yours.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/db4219e5637a8d4439744c134fa0b999.poster.avif?t=1750039177\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/db4219e5637a8d4439744c134fa0b999.webm?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/db4219e5637a8d4439744c134fa0b999.mp4?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Gameplay Overview</strong><br>The Demon Sword, Lux, offers a wide array of utilities. Not only can she perform powerful attacks and shield you from harm, but she can also act as a platform and restore objects from the past. Use your demonic companion to survive in a desolate, demon-ridden Osaka.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/45346a6640e0f9437e4e660b3a0d927e.poster.avif?t=1750039177\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/45346a6640e0f9437e4e660b3a0d927e.webm?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/45346a6640e0f9437e4e660b3a0d927e.mp4?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As Shin defeats demons and levels up, new skills can be unlocked via the skill tree. Unlock the \"Warp\" skill to travel anywhere on the map or the double-jump skill to get up to higher ledges and explore new locations with ease.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/dd2c4415932a48feafb96c6fd1dc340c.poster.avif?t=1750039177\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/dd2c4415932a48feafb96c6fd1dc340c.webm?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/dd2c4415932a48feafb96c6fd1dc340c.mp4?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But Lux isn't the only weapon in your arsenal. In addition to firearms, Shin can also wield weapons such as greatswords and whips. Experiment with a variety of armaments and create your own style of combat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/d093b53b596a4da29330be61a7257fc6.poster.avif?t=1750039177\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/d093b53b596a4da29330be61a7257fc6.webm?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/d093b53b596a4da29330be61a7257fc6.mp4?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Enjoy the latest metroidvania from Team Ladybug, the team behind such acclaimed titles as \"Touhou Luna Nights\" and \"Record of Lodoss War: Deedlit in Wonder Labyrinth.\"<br><br>Explore a map far larger than past Team Ladybug projects, filled with side quests that both deepen your connection to and expand upon the world of \"Blade Chimera.\"<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/22318bf811e0f4988293ca97c51a129a.poster.avif?t=1750039177\" width=620 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/22318bf811e0f4988293ca97c51a129a.webm?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671230/extras/22318bf811e0f4988293ca97c51a129a.mp4?t=1750039177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The Story</strong><br>It all began with the sudden appearance of a ghastly demonic horde. Humans fought against ghouls and ghosts in what would later be known as the \"Demon War,\" and the world was changed forever.<br><br>Thirty years later, using their expertise in combating demons, a religious group called the \"Holy Union\" has carved out a small but stable enclave of survivors.",
